{"tid":1390687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淘寶撚-八號風球雨具討論","createTime":"2019-07-31T08:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:23:21.000Z","uid":241255,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb83fb9ac79a8acb0bb099b61a2200fba6ddeb57","tid":1390687,"uid":241255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"打風出門嘅雨具大家都好有研究同討論，不過出面橫風橫雨，最重要都係要有一把堅固嘅雨遮。 見冇乜人講，為免大家忽略左呢樣咁常見嘅野，所以係度介紹下<br />\n<br />\n最常見當然係縮骨遮，輕巧便攜，居家旅行必備良藥，不過而家出面橫風橫雨，用呢d遮好易一吹就反，用唔得幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://betterlivingmall.com/image/cache/catalog/product-image/NOL/Danke-Umbrella/DWZ1828_1-800x800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbetterlivingmall.com%2Fimage%2Fcache%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct-image%2FNOL%2FDanke-Umbrella%2FDWZ1828_1-800x800.jpg&h=e556244e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁知道出面落緊雨，出得門都會帶把長遮，通常用開都係呢仲八條骨嘅，唔太重，又擋到下風雨<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ikea.com/tw/zh/images/products/knalla-yu-san-hei-se__0711833_PE728511_S4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ikea.com%2Ftw%2Fzh%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fknalla-yu-san-hei-se__0711833_PE728511_S4.JPG&h=0c26078d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過講到要好好咁遮風擋雨，其實仲有一d款係有16條骨，甚至係24條骨嘅，香港我就唔知邊度有，不過祖國偉大嘅淘寶上面我就見過，一把都只係廿幾蚊人仔，運到黎香港都不過係四十蚊，真係隨時平過你係香港普普通通咁買一把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Ytbb9VW/sb1135-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FYtbb9VW%2Fsb1135-3.jpg&h=23860170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1v4xLt4/p0602164292578-item-b4ddxf4x0750x0779-m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F1v4xLt4%2Fp0602164292578-item-b4ddxf4x0750x0779-m.jpg&h=eb66bce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重就真係重左d,成0.6kg,比平時8骨嘅足足重左一倍，真係攞多陣都覺得攰，唔少心撞到都覺得痛,不過遇著8號風，有把結實d嘅遮真係安全好多,大大滴雨點射過黎都可以擋耐d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實只要有良好嘅準備，8號風出門，又有乜好怕喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e43dd30bca52810995b883985600e02ca3fe602","tid":1390687,"uid":266874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:31:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c294a1450e75804357baed763700667a798820e","tid":1390687,"uid":241255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"有冇其他好物歡迎提議下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f92c28ebbd4b957aad5833fe77cc1e93b39594","tid":1390687,"uid":241255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:32:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8e674d266892a316aea4f89c28cd1c3672e6a0b","tid":1390687,"uid":241255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}